I"f<p>With the success of Mahabharata rerun, and the return of specials like Seinfeld, Parks and Rec, I am predicting a big market for nostalgia-as-a-service.Maybe we will even see the return of <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-H4GWUkdhps">old ads</a>.</p>

<p>With the world changing at an unprecedented level, with no guarantee about what the future holds, we are trying to hold on to familiar things.</p>

<p>And that includes things from the past which are tied to positive memories.</p>

